   Hôtels &
   préférence

Located between Blois and Chambord, Christophe Hay and Emmanuelle Hay welcome
you for a unique culinary experience.

   Within this gourmet restaurant Christophe Hay honors the Loire’s native
   products and the people who produce them to offer you a cuisine
   culturally rich and intentionally simple in an atmosphere decisively
   modern.

   From May 1 to September 1
   Restaurant closed Wednesday

   From September 2 to April 30
   Restaurant closed Tuesday and Wednesday

   Annual holiday

   From August 27 to September 2 2019 included
   From October 22 to 30 2019 included
   December 24 and 25 2019
   From February 15 to March 11 2020 included

